          "text": "本督，姓周名瑜字公瑾。吴侯驾前为臣，官拜水军都督之职。昨日天子有诏到\n来，封俺为南郡太守。想这南郡，乃是荆州统辖之地，可恨刘备，借去荆州，\n屡次讨取不还，吾不免再令鲁大夫过江催问。\n来，鲁大夫进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "中军",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁大夫进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为国辛劳用机谋，不知干戈几时休。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见都督！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫少礼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤肃进账，有何军情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因刘备借去荆州，屡次不还，令人可恼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启都督：前番鲁肃过江，他曾言道“等待他夺了西川，必将荆州送还东吴”。\n现有文约在此，都督何必着急？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当初所立文约，乃是孔明诡计，蒙哄于你。他既说夺取西川，为何不兴兵发\n马？此乃有意欺吾。叫吾等到何时？就命大夫过江去见刘备，看他是怎样回答！"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听本督一令："
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "论文约本是那诸葛诡计，\n他言道取西川本是推词。\n也免得我两家又动兵机。"
        },
        {
          "character": "此一番过江去把荆州来取、鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "周都督言和语肃当遵命，\n我只得再讨取荆州城。\n怕的是说不过南阳孔明。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "鲁子敬他生来老成持重，\n屡次里中诸葛诡计牢笼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套同退下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "待等鲁肃信回程。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "中军→鲁肃",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "鲁肃→周瑜",
