    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "周瑜",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、中军引周瑜同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "旌旗遮掩柴桑郡，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三番两次来奔命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见都督。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫回来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荆州之事何如？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都督容禀："
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "都督不必问其情，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你又中诸葛之计也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想当初刘备依刘表之时，常有吞并荆襄之意，何况西川刘璋乎！他今如此推诿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事到如今，都督有何妙策救我鲁肃？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾倒有一妙策在此，只是还须大夫一行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都督有何妙策？肃当遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫不必去见吴侯。再去荆州，对那刘备言讲，就说“孙刘两家，既结亲眷，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想那西川，山高路远，取之非易。都督此计，断断不可！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子敬！你真乃是忠厚长者也。你道我真取西川与他不成？我无非以此为名，明"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是我要取西川郡，"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "好一个聪明周公瑾，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "胸中妙计安排定，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "周瑜→鲁肃",
          "turns": 8
        },
        {
          "edge": "鲁肃→周瑜",
          "turns": 8
        }
      ],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 6,
