    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众人",
        "刘备",
        "四龙套",
        "探子",
        "诸葛亮",
        "赵云",
        "鲁肃"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套引刘备、诸葛亮同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁肃过江东吴转，"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪怕周郎计多端。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "探子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鲁肃过江来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（探子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，先生，鲁肃为何他又来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那鲁肃必然是未回东吴、见过吴侯，只到柴桑，与周瑜又商量什么计策，前来\n诱我。主公见了鲁肃，只看我点头，主公便满口应承，山人自有道理。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请鲁大夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四龙套",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请鲁大夫！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，皇叔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。刘备、鲁肃同坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "肃见了吴侯，诉说皇叔之意，吴侯甚称皇叔盛德；遂与诸将商议，今日孙刘结\n亲，自是一家。吴侯要起兵，替皇叔收川，却换荆州当做嫁资。但是军马自此\n经过，却要应会些钱粮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此说来，难得吴侯一番美意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此事全仗大夫美言，不胜感谢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "雄师到日，必要远道犒劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "告辞了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "辞别皇叔出营门，\n准备钱粮犒三军。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见鲁肃出营门，\n再与先生把话论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但不知周瑜又是何计？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周郎这小儿，死期近矣！此计就是欺瞒三尺之童，也难瞒过。此乃是假途灭虢\n之意。虚言收川，实取荆州。等主公出城劳军之时，乘势拿下，杀入城中，攻\n其不备也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生怎样准备？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四将军进帐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四将军进帐！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "冲锋对垒立战功，孙、曹闻名胆怕惊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见主公、先生！"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周郎要替主公收川，乃是假途灭虢之计。要叫主公出城犒军，趁此杀害，即夺\n荆州。山人同主公，暂到公安。就命将军带领五千人马埋伏城中，偃旗息鼓；\n等周瑜到来，竖起枪刀，将他诡计道破。不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番周瑜虽不即死，也要九分无气也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "准备窝弓擒猛虎，\n安排香铒钓鳌鱼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
