          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐盛、丁奉、周泰、凌统、陈武、甘宁同上，同起霸。〖点绛唇〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐盛、丁奉、周泰、凌统、陈武、甘宁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺——"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐盛",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐盛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁奉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丁奉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周泰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "周泰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "凌统",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凌统。"
        },
        {
          "character": "陈武",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陈武。"
        },
        {
          "character": "甘宁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "甘宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁奉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！今日都督升帐，你我两厢侍候！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐盛、周泰、凌统、陈武、甘宁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。〖大吹打〗。八龙套、四下手、中军引周瑜、鲁肃同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "暗设机谋，统貔貅，夺取荆州。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐盛、丁奉、周泰、凌统、陈武、甘宁同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐盛、丁奉、周泰、凌统、陈武、甘宁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见都督。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站立两厢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐盛、丁奉、周泰、凌统、陈武、甘宁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄公三略吕六韬，将令一出山岳摇。假意兴兵西川道，杀却刘备气方消。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "本督，周瑜。适才子敬归来，言道刘备准备钱粮犒赏军士；不免就地发兵。\n嘟，众将官，兵发荆州！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖泣颜回〗。周瑜坐高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上得船来，好一派江景！诸葛亮吓，孔明！你此番也中本督之计也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人言诸葛诡计巧，今日看来也不高。刘备出城把军犒，定中本督计笼牢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐盛、丁奉、周泰、凌统、陈武、甘宁",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启都督：此地已离荆州不远。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓！一路之上，并不见有一人。\n众将官，带马同到城外。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同大转场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何城楼之上这样静悄悄的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莫非又中了孔明之计了吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大夫前去叫城。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！开城！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（赵云上城楼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何人叫城？"
        },
        {
          "character": "鲁肃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东吴周都督到此。你是何人答话？"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃常山赵子龙也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（鲁肃退。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "赵云",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问都督到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周瑜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾替你主来取西川，难道你"
        }
      ],
